snippet.title: Boom! Preparing for Fireworks with Vet Amber Batson
snippet.description:
Why are some dogs afraid of fireworks? Why is it that some appear to be ok with them and then become afraid? How can we help cats, dogs and horses deal with fireworks. In this interview we discuss all of these questions.
